channel.title: H?kina Te M?nuka
channel.desc: NEW: The wh?nau set up a surprise birthday for their Nanny Del, and as they write her song, they reflect on how singing & music has always been a huge part of their lives. And lead voice of Coco Reo M?ori, M?nuera and his wh?nau perform at a screening of the movie, celebrating Te Wiki o te Reo M?ori.
